+Faithful-transmission MIDI uses a separate whole-file handoff instead of that
+fragment-selection path. Processed faithful manifests now carry
+`faithful_scene`: a tracker-like scene payload with one `faithful_midi` melody
+lane, ordered steps, exact imported MIDI `pitch`, exact source
